# Copy to simulation/.env and fill in <YOUR_API_KEY>. The Streamlit app
# reads SUBGRAPH_URL at startup and falls back to a synthetic GBM
# dataset if unset.
#
# Get a free Graph Network API key:
#   1. https://thegraph.com/studio/apikeys/  → sign in with wallet
#   2. Create an API Key. Free tier is 100k queries/month.
#
# The deployment ID below is the official Uniswap V3 subgraph on Base,
# listed at https://developers.uniswap.org/docs/ecosystem/subgraphs/overview
# (source: Uniswap/uniswap-docs, docs/api/subgraph/overview.md).
#
# SUBGRAPH_URL=https://gateway.thegraph.com/api/<YOUR_API_KEY>/subgraphs/id/43Hwfi3dJSoGpyas9VwNoDAv55yjgGrPpNSmbQZArzMG
